      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she's a real beauty. This car is in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one\u2014always garage-kept and meticulously cared for. You won't find a single blemish on it, and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm only letting it go because our family is growing, but I'd love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
