    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) finished in collector-quality Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system. Power is managed by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a Variable M Differential Lock for superior lateral traction. The chassis retains its factory torsional rigidity with a documented subframe inspection and reinforced mounting points. Mechanically impeccable, the vehicle exhibits a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline, supported by a pristine cooling system and recent rod bearing service. This is a turn-key, museum-quality example with zero deferred maintenance, offering the raw, analog feedback sought by purists.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Pristine condition. Garage kept. No scratches or dents. Clean title. Mechanically perfect. Inspection welcome.",
