      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating, showing absolutely no chips, dings, or scratches. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any wear, and the interior has remained strictly smoke-free. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intuitive climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history from authorized dealers and a whisper-quiet engine that performs exactly as it did on the showroom floor. Garage-kept and driven only in fair weather, this is arguably the finest example currently available on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
